      "message": "I want to prevent other projects from being able to export logs to a cloud project owned by someone else.\n\nLet\u0027s say that CrOS and Chromium granted monitoring writer role to logdog@appspot.googleservice.com. Then, Fuchsia can update their project config to export their logs to Chromium and CrOS projects.\n\nHowever, I don\u0027t think this prevent such a thing from happening at all. Fuchsia can still update their project configs with Chromium\u0027s exporter_svc_account. Any suggestions are welcome. :)",
